data.description: Not many homes become available in Gueydan so don't miss out on this 3 bedroom, 3 bath home that features two living areas and a huge 550 sq ft bonus room (originally a garage) that can be used for home office, small home business, mother-n-law suite -- very flexible space as it has window unit and sink/plumbing.  The breezeway porch leads you from the front yard to the back yard and double carport.  Country kitchen with walk in pantry/laundry room is open to smaller living room (or dining room).  Downstairs has office area that was a bedroom and can be converted back to 4th bedroom with the addition of a wall with own bathroom.  Upstairs in a bedroom/bath suite and 2 additional bedrooms and bath.   Stove to remain.
